dcterms:description: The Foursquares spatio-temporal dataset contains users' check-in records in the Pittsburgh area between 24/02/2012 and 24/05/2012, composed of the number of check-ins by 121 users belonging to 15 different types of venues over 1198 time periods, resulting in a 3rd order tensor.
dcterms:title: Foursquares spatio-temporal dataset

dcterms:creator: K. Mohaddes

dcterms:description: The macroeconomic panel dataset is a subsample of quarterly data from 1979Q2 to 2016Q4, including variables such as real GDP growth, inflation rate, equity price index log-returns, exchange rate log-returns, and interest rates for 19 countries.
dcterms:title: Macroeconomic panel dataset
